snippet: Rafa Nadal continued his resurgence with a thrilling 2-6 6-4 6-2 victory over world number two Andy Murray on Saturday to set up a Monte Carlo Masters final against Gael Monfils....
lead_paragraph: Rafa Nadal continued his resurgence with a thrilling 2-6 6-4 6-2 victory over world number two Andy Murray on Saturday to set up a Monte Carlo Masters final against Gael Monfils.

headline.print_headline: Nadal Sinks Murray to Reach Final With Monfils
headline.main: Nadal Sinks Murray to Reach Final With Monfils
